c0000000
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:03.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We lack the information</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:03.420 --> 00:00:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to make a conclusion.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:05.010 --> 00:00:06.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should consider
the possibility</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:06.670 --> 00:00:08.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that it doesn't have a mind.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:11.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only way to defeat it
may well be with brute force.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:12.930 --> 00:00:14.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think you can do that?</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:14.720 --> 00:00:16.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, who can say?</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:17.390 --> 00:00:18.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:23.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Um, if that's our plan,</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it might have to be me.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:26.030 --> 00:00:28.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I may be able to kill
Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:28.990 --> 00:00:29.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Oh?
-[FERN] Yes.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Splendid.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let the strategizing begin.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:20.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:20.730 --> 00:02:23.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] To confirm,
if my replica does have a mind,</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:23.730 --> 00:02:25.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll find Edel,
escort her here,</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:26.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and use hypnosis magic</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:26.810 --> 00:02:28.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to penetrate
my mental defenses.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:28.860 --> 00:02:30.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This will give Fern
the opening she needs.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:30.990 --> 00:02:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, she'll move in to combat</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-and kill me.
-[blood dripping]</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:35.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN] Perfect.
-That's a little callous.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:35.610 --> 00:02:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[panting]
-[METHODE] Mister Dunste.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:43.210 --> 00:02:44.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:47.330 --> 00:02:48.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where's Miss Edel?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:51.710 --> 00:02:53.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DUNSTE] We were attacked
by Sense's replica,</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:56.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she took herself
out of the competition.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:57.680 --> 00:03:00.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand. And Mister Blei?</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:00.140 --> 00:03:01.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:03.310 --> 00:03:05.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I made it this far
because he put himself</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:05.140 --> 00:03:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>between the monster and me.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:08.150 --> 00:03:10.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can only hope he got
out of here with his life.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:11.030 --> 00:03:13.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both panting]</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:16.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thumps]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:16.950 --> 00:03:18.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[clattering]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:19.990 --> 00:03:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keep moving! Leave me!</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:22.870 --> 00:03:25.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:26.790 --> 00:03:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, Blei!</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:28.380 --> 00:03:30.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BLEI] This way at least
one of us will pass.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:30.540 --> 00:03:33.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Blei panting]</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:39.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have some information.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:39.970 --> 00:03:41.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can we work together?</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:43.060 --> 00:03:44.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I've wanted</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:44.270 --> 00:03:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since the beginning
of this ordeal.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:47.850 --> 00:03:50.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there anyone
who can treat this man?</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:50.310 --> 00:03:51.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:53.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I always carry
a holy scripture.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:55.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A simple healing spell
won't be an issue.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:56.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Go ahead.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:56.820 --> 00:04:00.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:04.490 --> 00:04:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Well, that settles that.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:06.160 --> 00:04:08.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The copies don't have
minds after all.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:08.710 --> 00:04:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:09.880 --> 00:04:11.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Miss Edel tried
to hypnotize it,</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:14.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but discovered that while
they can precisely mimic</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:14.090 --> 00:04:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a mind's functions,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:15.380 --> 00:04:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the replicas do not possess
minds of their own.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:20.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes
our most painless strategy</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:20.760 --> 00:04:21.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>out of the question.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:22.890 --> 00:04:25.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose we must adjust
our plan accordingly.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why talk of plans, Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:28.810 --> 00:04:31.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is too much we don't know
to take them any further.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:33.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Before we continue,</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:33.650 --> 00:04:36.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we need to know exactly
what those replicas are</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:37.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and who created them.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:38.530 --> 00:04:39.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
We cannot defeat them</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:39.650 --> 00:04:41.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if their true nature
is a mystery.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The most important thing
we can learn</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:44.410 --> 00:04:46.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is if these copies have
any unique weaknesses.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:47.580 --> 00:04:49.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that thing's
as strong as Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:49.370 --> 00:04:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>people will probably die.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd happily take a hint.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:54.670 --> 00:04:56.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid I have no comment.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
Figured as much.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:58.760 --> 00:05:00.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] They don't
have any weaknesses.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:03.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The doubles are controlled
by the Spiegel,</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:04.300 --> 00:05:07.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a monster who's resided here
since the mythical era.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:07.850 --> 00:05:08.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Lawine.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:08.940 --> 00:05:10.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
How do you know that?</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:11.190 --> 00:05:12.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Courtesy of my eldest brother.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:13.270 --> 00:05:14.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was in the advance party</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:14.810 --> 00:05:16.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the Continental
Magic Association</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:16.780 --> 00:05:18.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>sent into the tomb.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:19.820 --> 00:05:21.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds to me like
you girls had a leg up.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:22.780 --> 00:05:24.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That explains how
you lasted this long.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:25.330 --> 00:05:26.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:26.910 --> 00:05:29.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, you made
a childish misstep.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:30.580 --> 00:05:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should've worked with us.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:32.420 --> 00:05:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That information would've been
more valuable in our hands.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:36.130 --> 00:05:38.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say you felt
very approachable</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:38.130 --> 00:05:39.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to us at the time.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:39.550 --> 00:05:41.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plus, Frieren and Fern
raced right in</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:41.380 --> 00:05:42.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before we had the chance
to team up.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:43.390 --> 00:05:44.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
Have you seen yourself?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:45.220 --> 00:05:47.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't trust
a middle-aged egoist like you</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:49.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not to abandon you allies.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:49.310 --> 00:05:50.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anybody would
doubt your motives.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:53.020 --> 00:05:53.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Richter chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:53.980 --> 00:05:55.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] She really
doesn't like you, huh?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:56.190 --> 00:05:58.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While middle-aged
is technically true,</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:58.940 --> 00:06:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's something
about having it thrown</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:01.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in your face that stings.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:04.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you think you should
apologize to him?</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:04.610 --> 00:06:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm very sorry, Pops.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:06.370 --> 00:06:07.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:08.910 --> 00:06:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to the Advance
party's observation report,</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Spiegel is close.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:13.620 --> 00:06:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's locked
in the treasure room</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:15.250 --> 00:06:17.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just on the other side
of that hall.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The monster itself is weak</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:19.670 --> 00:06:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and has no way
of attacking us directly.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:23.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once we defeat it,</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:24.090 --> 00:06:26.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all the replicas
will cease to be.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:31.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That aligns with what our
mana detection has revealed.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:31.390 --> 00:06:32.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:33.140 --> 00:06:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which bring us back
to the issue of the door.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:35.850 --> 00:06:38.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's shut fast with
an incredible sealing spell</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:38.320 --> 00:06:39.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>mightier than most I've seen.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:40.570 --> 00:06:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can confirm
the seal is quite the puzzle,</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:43.450 --> 00:06:45.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and almost certainly
my replica's work.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:46.990 --> 00:06:49.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a spell that shuts
the door of a treasure vault</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:49.410 --> 00:06:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the risk of your life.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:51.540 --> 00:06:53.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of the highest rated
sealing spells</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the world of folk magic.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:55.870 --> 00:06:58.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That door will not open
until the caster is dead.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:59.250 --> 00:07:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:00.630 --> 00:07:02.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The simplest option
would be to ignore the door</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:02.840 --> 00:07:03.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and break down the wall,</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:04.550 --> 00:07:06.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I have to assume
they accounted for that.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:06.760 --> 00:07:07.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:09.100 --> 00:07:10.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talk of doors and seals?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:11.100 --> 00:07:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm more concerned with
the overpowered doppelganger</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:13.770 --> 00:07:16.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that still stands between us
and the Spiegel.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:17.230 --> 00:07:19.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we want a fair shot at it,
we should hurry.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:21.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And why might that be?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:22.150 --> 00:07:24.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As you've witnessed,
the Spiegel guards itself</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:24.900 --> 00:07:27.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by creating copies
of those within the dungeon.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:28.120 --> 00:07:29.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As time passes by,</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:29.740 --> 00:07:31.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they slowly begin
to trickle down</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:31.370 --> 00:07:33.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the bottom of the labyrinth
to protect it.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:35.870 --> 00:07:37.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aside from my brother's unit,</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:37.870 --> 00:07:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>most of the Advance party died.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:39.790 --> 00:07:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Many in this exact spot.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:42.050 --> 00:07:43.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:44.050 --> 00:07:45.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They died
with victory in sight,</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:46.130 --> 00:07:47.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just before they reached
the bottom.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:50.260 --> 00:07:51.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:51.810 --> 00:07:52.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:54.470 --> 00:07:56.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Valuable information.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:56.310 --> 00:07:57.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Excuse me.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:58.150 --> 00:07:59.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The replicas
mimic the functions</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:59.850 --> 00:08:02.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the original's mind
very closely, yes?</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:02.860 --> 00:08:06.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That means the flesh
and blood's vulnerabilities</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:06.200 --> 00:08:07.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should show up in their double.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:08.610 --> 00:08:09.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would think so.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:11.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:11.740 --> 00:08:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that much is true,
we may have a real chance.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:15.620 --> 00:08:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And just what flaw
are you thinking of?</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:21.170 --> 00:08:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:08:23.170 --> 00:08:24.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need you
to stand by that wall</b></Default>

c0000167
00:08:24.670 --> 00:08:25.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a moment, please.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:08:26.170 --> 00:08:27.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:35.470 --> 00:08:37.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:37.140 --> 00:08:38.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rumbling]
-[Denken gasps]</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:46.570 --> 00:08:47.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can't be.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:48.780 --> 00:08:49.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Incredible.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:08:49.900 --> 00:08:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't believe my eyes.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:08:52.490 --> 00:08:53.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did everyone notice?</b></Default>

c0000175
00:08:55.030 --> 00:08:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What are we looking at?
-No clue.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:08:57.750 --> 00:08:59.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
I didn't think it existed.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:08:59.420 --> 00:09:01.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is Frieren's
fatal vulnerability.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:02.210 --> 00:09:05.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did I let this slip past me
when we battled before?</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:07.260 --> 00:09:09.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My preconceptions about
how an experienced mage</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:11.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be blinded
me to the truth.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:12.340 --> 00:09:13.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:14.140 --> 00:09:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Every time
that she casts a spell,</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:16.180 --> 00:09:17.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her mana detection
is interrupted</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:17.770 --> 00:09:19.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a fraction of a second.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:19.850 --> 00:09:21.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN] But isn't that
a common mistake</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:23.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>made by apprentice mages?</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:25.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have never been
very good about it.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:26.230 --> 00:09:27.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you were aware of this,</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:27.690 --> 00:09:29.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why didn't you bother
mentioning it?</b></Default>

c0000190
00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:32.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's mortifying,
to say the least.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:09:32.530 --> 00:09:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] This is not the time
to be embarrassed.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:09:35.740 --> 00:09:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still, though.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:09:36.870 --> 00:09:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's highly skilled
in every other area</b></Default>

c0000194
00:09:38.950 --> 00:09:40.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you can imagine.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I doubt
there are many mages</b></Default>

c0000196
00:09:42.620 --> 00:09:44.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who could exploit
that vulnerability.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:09:45.250 --> 00:09:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] In any case,
let's discuss our strategy.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:09:48.550 --> 00:09:55.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000199
00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:59.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:04.690 --> 00:10:07.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000201
00:10:11.030 --> 00:10:12.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
Even if we can somehow</b></Default>

c0000202
00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:13.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>handle Frieren's replica,</b></Default>

c0000203
00:10:13.610 --> 00:10:15.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-what about the rest?
-[FERN] Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:15.700 --> 00:10:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You seem to be
enjoying yourself.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:10:17.870 --> 00:10:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-I fear they will gather</b></Default>

c0000206
00:10:18.990 --> 00:10:20.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before we can do it in.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000208
00:10:24.460 --> 00:10:26.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000209
00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:29.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go over it once more.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:30.130 --> 00:10:32.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Firstly, Eisen will draw
the enemy his way,</b></Default>

c0000211
00:10:32.550 --> 00:10:33.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I'll attack from the flank.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:10:33.970 --> 00:10:34.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:37.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you come in
with supporting fire.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:10:37.510 --> 00:10:38.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Heiter?</b></Default>

c0000215
00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:40.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
He gets the day off.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:10:40.470 --> 00:10:41.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's hungover.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:43.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
He's dead.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:10:44.060 --> 00:10:45.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[growls]
-[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000219
00:10:46.520 --> 00:10:47.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000220
00:10:47.860 --> 00:10:49.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

c0000221
00:10:49.690 --> 00:10:50.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thumps]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000222
00:10:51.530 --> 00:10:53.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000223
00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:55.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000224
00:10:56.660 --> 00:10:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000225
00:10:58.280 --> 00:10:59.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[slashing]
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000226
00:11:01.290 --> 00:11:02.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000227
00:11:03.750 --> 00:11:04.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This meeting.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It reminds me
of the many whispers</b></Default>

c0000229
00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:08.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my party exchanged in dungeons.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:09.130 --> 00:11:16.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:32.150 --> 00:11:33.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now...</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:35.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll let our plan
speak for itself.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:36.700 --> 00:11:37.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think we can win?</b></Default>

c0000234
00:11:38.570 --> 00:11:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you worry.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:42.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There doesn't exist a dungeon
that can't be conquered.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:46.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And as I'm the mage
of the party that cleared</b></Default>

c0000237
00:11:46.210 --> 00:11:48.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>more dungeons than
any other in history,</b></Default>

c0000238
00:11:48.290 --> 00:11:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm an authority on the matter.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:11:52.960 --> 00:11:55.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you two sure
you don't need any help</b></Default>

c0000240
00:11:55.130 --> 00:11:56.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fighting Frieren's replica?</b></Default>

c0000241
00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:59.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're all ready and more
than willing to join the fray.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:00.350 --> 00:12:01.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fewer of us
there are inside,</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:01.970 --> 00:12:04.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the easier it will be
to predict its movements.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:04.350 --> 00:12:05.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:06.060 --> 00:12:07.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we all entered
the battle at once,</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:07.810 --> 00:12:09.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our victory would be
nearly guaranteed,</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:10.360 --> 00:12:12.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but most of us would
die in the process.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:12:13.610 --> 00:12:15.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I doubt we would
even have the time</b></Default>

c0000249
00:12:15.110 --> 00:12:16.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to use our escape golems.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:12:17.660 --> 00:12:18.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need us here.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:12:19.320 --> 00:12:21.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Without anyone
to slow down the replicas</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:22.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as they make
their way to the bottom,</b></Default>

c0000253
00:12:22.580 --> 00:12:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they would quickly
outnumber you.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:12:29.250 --> 00:12:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If they surround us,</b></Default>

c0000255
00:12:30.420 --> 00:12:32.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nobody will make it out
of this dungeon alive.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:12:34.340 --> 00:12:35.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Follow our plan closely.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:12:36.300 --> 00:12:37.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
We will.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:38.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good luck in there.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:12:42.470 --> 00:12:43.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Open the door.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:12:44.010 --> 00:12:45.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000261
00:12:45.470 --> 00:12:52.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000262
00:12:58.150 --> 00:13:00.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:00.570 --> 00:13:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:03.830 --> 00:13:04.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, then...</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:05.370 --> 00:13:07.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who in this test
would each of you</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be the most concerned
to meet on a battlefield?</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:10.830 --> 00:13:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:32.650 --> 00:13:35.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:36.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Judradjim.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:36.940 --> 00:13:38.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thunder rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:39.530 --> 00:13:40.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:41.570 --> 00:13:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] It's behaving just like
Mistress Frieren predicted.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:44.410 --> 00:13:47.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thunder rumbling]
-[crackling]</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:48.450 --> 00:13:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000275
00:14:01.170 --> 00:14:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Vollzanbel.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:14:02.300 --> 00:14:04.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

c0000277
00:14:04.800 --> 00:14:06.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It's mana detection broke off.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:14:07.310 --> 00:14:09.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My double would be
on the lookout for Fern,</b></Default>

c0000279
00:14:09.270 --> 00:14:11.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who took that opportunity
to hide.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:14:12.390 --> 00:14:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But its hands
are full dealing with</b></Default>

c0000281
00:14:13.980 --> 00:14:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the equally matched
opponent before it.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:14:16.900 --> 00:14:18.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can't afford
to think about Fern.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:14:21.110 --> 00:14:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all...</b></Default>

c0000284
00:14:23.410 --> 00:14:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no one knows better than I do
how frightening I can be.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:26.490 --> 00:14:30.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:30.870 --> 00:14:31.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You'll be all right.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:32.580 --> 00:14:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even I can't detect you easily.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:34.790 --> 00:14:37.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the heat of battle,
my copy won't have a chance.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:38.170 --> 00:14:40.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once I'm hidden and able
to land a solid attack,</b></Default>

c0000290
00:14:41.010 --> 00:14:42.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're sure
it should be Zoltraak?</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:43.170 --> 00:14:45.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the quickest spell,
therefore the best we've got.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:46.470 --> 00:14:47.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:47.510 --> 00:14:49.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides that, for us elves,</b></Default>

c0000294
00:14:49.470 --> 00:14:51.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zoltraak's only been
in the picture</b></Default>

c0000295
00:14:51.180 --> 00:14:52.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a relatively short time.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We haven't been around
the spell long enough</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:55.060 --> 00:14:56.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to reflexively
defend against it.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:58.270 --> 00:15:00.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not to say it'll stop us
dead in our tracks.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:15:01.070 --> 00:15:03.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It takes only a moment
for us to respond.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:15:04.110 --> 00:15:06.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the time we spend
thinking causes a delay.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:15:07.570 --> 00:15:08.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're different, though.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:15:09.030 --> 00:15:10.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000303
00:15:10.330 --> 00:15:12.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Zoltraak has existed
since you were born.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:15.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To you, it's something
that has always been,</b></Default>

c0000305
00:15:15.460 --> 00:15:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a fundamental part of mage-hood
engraved into your very being.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:19.460 --> 00:15:22.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:22.170 --> 00:15:24.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt that
your Zoltraak can kill me.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:26.300 --> 00:15:28.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hit it with every last drop
of mana you've got.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:28.890 --> 00:15:30.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:30.510 --> 00:15:33.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:33.430 --> 00:15:37.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:46.030 --> 00:15:47.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:48.070 --> 00:15:50.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was under the impression
that you didn't like me.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:52.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised to see you
in this place.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:15:53.700 --> 00:15:56.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, I would've
wagered you</b></Default>

c0000316
00:15:56.080 --> 00:15:57.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I would never meet again.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The reason I'm here
is to deliver my master's will.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:03.670 --> 00:16:05.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fifty years have passed.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:07.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:07.840 --> 00:16:09.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Flamme has died.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:10.640 --> 00:16:11.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not sad?</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:13.060 --> 00:16:14.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only trained
the girl on a whim.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:16:15.310 --> 00:16:16.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[paper rustling]</b></Default>

c0000324
00:16:21.820 --> 00:16:23.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's practically a report.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:24.320 --> 00:16:25.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
What does it say?</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:26.650 --> 00:16:29.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Emperor has authorized
nationwide magical research</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:29.740 --> 00:16:31.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the advice of Flamme.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:32.830 --> 00:16:34.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until very recently,</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:34.490 --> 00:16:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>human societies
have written magic off</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:36.410 --> 00:16:37.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as the stuff of demons.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:38.290 --> 00:16:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Therefore, studying it openly
was strictly forbidden.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:42.080 --> 00:16:44.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Flamme encouraged him
to change that.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:44.500 --> 00:16:46.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before her death,
she had been training</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:46.170 --> 00:16:49.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a newly established unit
she calls the Imperial Mages.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:51.220 --> 00:16:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it says right here</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:52.800 --> 00:16:54.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she wants me
to take it over for her.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:57.350 --> 00:16:59.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a greedy woman she was.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:17:00.560 --> 00:17:02.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Receiving authorization
to study magic</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:02.810 --> 00:17:04.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is an enormous feat,</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:04.730 --> 00:17:06.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but still she wants more.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:06.990 --> 00:17:09.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Is what she did
really so impressive?</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:12.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She has filled the largest
empire with a hunger.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:12.820 --> 00:17:14.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They want to study magic,</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:14.660 --> 00:17:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and even adopt the craft
for military use.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:18.080 --> 00:17:20.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The neighboring nations
are sure to respond.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:20.580 --> 00:17:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a few short decades,</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:22.330 --> 00:17:24.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>magic will spread
throughout the continent.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:26.130 --> 00:17:27.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We stand
at the precipice of an era</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:28.010 --> 00:17:29.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in which magic will be for all.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:31.010 --> 00:17:32.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not long from now,</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:34.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>humanity will acquire
the strength to fight back</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:35.050 --> 00:17:37.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>against the Demon King
and his forces.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:38.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, my.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:40.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is impressive. I see now.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:41.560 --> 00:17:42.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Impressive.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:43.400 --> 00:17:44.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[paper rustling]</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:45.110 --> 00:17:47.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rustling]
-Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:47.400 --> 00:17:49.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, that is not
the future I want.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:17:51.110 --> 00:17:52.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Begone, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:53.660 --> 00:17:56.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I cannot comply
with this final request.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:56.580 --> 00:17:58.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find it displeasing.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:17:58.700 --> 00:17:59.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:02.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An era in which
anyone can use magic?</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:03.750 --> 00:18:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic should be
revered and respected.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:07.130 --> 00:18:09.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I refuse to teach anyone
who lacks talent.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:12.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
How dare she send this to me?</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:12.930 --> 00:18:15.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Flamme and I never could
understand each other.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:16.510 --> 00:18:17.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I get.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:18.100 --> 00:18:20.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one student
I trained on a whim.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:20.600 --> 00:18:21.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
She predicted this.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:25.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My master warned me that
you would probably get upset</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:25.230 --> 00:18:26.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and tear her will to pieces.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:18:29.440 --> 00:18:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she wanted me
to deliver this regardless.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:18:32.610 --> 00:18:34.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said her dream came true.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:18:35.200 --> 00:18:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It didn't make
much sense to me.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:38.870 --> 00:18:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:41.330 --> 00:18:42.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I'm going to leave now.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:44.080 --> 00:18:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I doubt we'll ever meet again.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:46.580 --> 00:18:47.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:49.760 --> 00:18:51.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before you go,
let's take a walk.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:18:52.510 --> 00:18:53.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at the two of us.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:18:53.970 --> 00:18:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have all the time
in the world.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:18:58.060 --> 00:18:59.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water drips]</b></Default>

c0000384
00:18:59.720 --> 00:19:02.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] An era in which
anyone can use magic.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:02.770 --> 00:19:04.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She had quite the dream, huh?</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:06.100 --> 00:19:07.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I doubt it was nobly dreamt.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:08.150 --> 00:19:09.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When she first
pondered the idea,</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:09.780 --> 00:19:12.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she wasn't considering
security or self-defense.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:13.280 --> 00:19:15.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or the Demon King
and his forces.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:20.490 --> 00:19:23.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did she ever tell you
what her favorite spell was?</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:24.210 --> 00:19:26.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One that created
a field of flowers.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:27.830 --> 00:19:30.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was useless at best,
and foolish at worst.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:30.710 --> 00:19:36.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:36.630 --> 00:19:39.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] She loved magic
with the whole of her being.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:19:39.890 --> 00:19:42.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She genuinely wanted
everyone in the world</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:42.180 --> 00:19:43.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to experience it,</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:43.810 --> 00:19:45.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even in its
most frivolous forms.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:47.190 --> 00:19:48.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I found that repulsive.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:19:49.940 --> 00:19:52.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It sounded like
the fanciful dream of a child.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:19:53.280 --> 00:19:55.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But no.
It lasted all her years.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:19:56.740 --> 00:19:58.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remember the first time
she described</b></Default>

c0000402
00:19:58.700 --> 00:20:00.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this lofty aspiration.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:00.450 --> 00:20:02.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was a girl,
small in stature</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:02.580 --> 00:20:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but great in spirits.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest,</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:07.420 --> 00:20:09.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't think she would live
to see such an era.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:10.460 --> 00:20:13.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I never would've guessed
she'd bring it on herself.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:16.970 --> 00:20:18.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I looked at her,</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:18.630 --> 00:20:21.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I saw a life so short
it was practically nothing.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:22.010 --> 00:20:25.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet in her time, she founded
humanity's magic.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:25.890 --> 00:20:28.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My master made decisions
more quickly than carefully,</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:29.650 --> 00:20:32.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like she was always hurrying
along to the next thing.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:34.730 --> 00:20:36.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Humans have limited life spans.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:37.070 --> 00:20:39.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They exist much closer
to death than we do.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:41.530 --> 00:20:42.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Throughout our lives,</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:43.080 --> 00:20:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we are all faced with a series
of important decisions.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:20:46.450 --> 00:20:47.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But unlike you and I,</b></Default>

c0000418
00:20:48.120 --> 00:20:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>humans cannot afford
to delay them.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:20:52.590 --> 00:20:53.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we don't have an answer,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:20:53.880 --> 00:20:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we can take a century
or two to find one.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:20:56.880 --> 00:20:59.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can ignore our decisions
for a millennium</b></Default>

c0000422
00:20:59.130 --> 00:21:00.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we so choose.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:02.340 --> 00:21:04.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We hardly have life spans.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:04.220 --> 00:21:06.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're more like eternities.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:08.480 --> 00:21:09.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:09.440 --> 00:21:11.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took humanity
countless centuries</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and seas of sweat and blood</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:13.230 --> 00:21:15.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to build the civilization
they have now.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:16.320 --> 00:21:17.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From this point forward,</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:17.530 --> 00:21:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>their progress
will only accelerate.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:20.610 --> 00:21:22.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:23.200 --> 00:21:24.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
A mere 1,000 years.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:26.370 --> 00:21:28.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is when the era
of humans will arrive.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:34.540 --> 00:21:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
They will surely overtake us.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:39.470 --> 00:21:43.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:43.550 --> 00:21:46.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So don't neglect
your training, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:48.770 --> 00:21:49.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000439
00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:53.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000440
00:21:53.940 --> 00:21:58.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000441
00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:00.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For if anyone cuts
your long life short,</b></Default>

c0000442
00:22:01.110 --> 00:22:03.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it will be
the Demon King himself.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:05.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000444
00:22:05.370 --> 00:22:07.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or it will be a human mage.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:22:07.410 --> 00:22:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000446
00:22:12.120 --> 00:22:14.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That excites me, Serie.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:22:16.500 --> 00:22:18.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything we've known,</b></Default>

c0000448
00:22:18.590 --> 00:22:20.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the entire world
of magic and mages,</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:21.840 --> 00:22:23.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is about to be born anew.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:23.630 --> 00:22:29.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:32.690 --> 00:22:39.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:39.730 --> 00:22:40.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000453
00:22:40.940 --> 00:22:47.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000454
00:24:20.290 --> 00:24:22.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Now, let's end this.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:24:22.500 --> 00:24:24.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Incredible, Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] We expected
this much. I suppose I have</b></Default>

c0000457
00:24:26.420 --> 00:24:27.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no choice.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:24:27.550 --> 00:24:29.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] So,
this is the height of magic.</b></Default>

